<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>AI Content Creation | Julia Alix</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />

  <style>
    .email-template-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 28px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .email-template-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(255, 111, 145, 0.16);
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    }

    .email-template-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 55px rgba(255, 111, 145, 0.22);
    }

    .email-template-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 18px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .email-template-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <a href="index.html" class="logo">☾ Julia Alix</a>

    <nav>
      <a href="index.html#work">Work</a>
      <a href="index.html#about">About</a>
      <a href="index.html#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="inner-hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">SENIOR DESIGNER</p>
      <h1>AI Content Creation</h1>
      <p>
        Here are few of my AI Content Creations inspired using Klaviyo Templates.
      </p>

      <img src="Moon.png" alt="Julia Alix avatar" class="inner-avatar" />
    </section>

    <section class="work-section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Email Template Designs</h2>
        <p>AI-generated content visuals presented in a simple two-column layout.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="email-template-grid">
        <div class="email-template-card">
          <img src="Email_1.jpg" alt="AI generated email template design 1" />
        </div>

        <div class="email-template-card">
          <img src="Email_2.jpg" alt="AI generated email template design 2" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    © Julia Jasmin Alix. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
